{"tid":930033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國參議員盧比奧 對華為太子女被捕表示歡迎","createTime":"2018-12-06T04:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T12:33:02.000Z","uid":5195,"like":100,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b6b93c1a63cbe49b12f4bf9314c919cbdacb529f","tid":930033,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:20:14.000Z","msg":"加拿大傳媒報道，中國科技龍頭華為創辦人任正非長女、副董事長兼首席財務官（CFO）孟晚舟，因涉嫌違反美國對伊朗的貿易制裁，於本月1日在加拿大溫哥華國際機場被捕。有美國參議員對此表示歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大《環球郵報》5日報道稱，美國共和黨參議員盧比奧（Marco Rubio）稱讚加拿大逮捕華為財務總監孟晚舟。他還再次呼籲加拿大總理杜魯多（Justin Trudeau）封殺華為5G技術。盧比奧於聲明中說，歡迎加拿大政府逮捕華為CFO，她有可能違反了美國對伊朗的制裁令，「我敦促立即將她引渡到美國。」 他還說，華為同中國政府和中共有直接聯繫，對美國國家安全構成嚴重威脅。"},{"pid":"61458083fe74ebbda81621e49fc3051e36fb0c82","tid":930033,"uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:22:25.000Z","msg":"去左美國真係唔洗走"},{"pid":"fcd18023f1867300c653260bdf1a29a0eb7fbf47","tid":930033,"uid":209487,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:24:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0c316256e69e3a0cf544f8f2c530dafedc1b232","tid":930033,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fcd18023f1867300c653260bdf1a29a0eb7fbf47","tid":930033,"uid":209487,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:24:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:26:40.000Z","msg":"我ＣＡＬＬ小鳳姐祝賀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89bce8b9a9c2ac01f1c609e20d68642f977856f0","tid":930033,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:27:31.000Z","msg":"我代表一箱西瓜表示歡迎"},{"pid":"55e1b6350ff16229eba6b864bde0a4dd3d4a2250","tid":930033,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:27:50.000Z","msg":"表示歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f8987f402e9cc06de9d2fa4f8cab0f10d5b86e","tid":930033,"uid":82052,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"61458083fe74ebbda81621